DATABASE TABLES FOR VA WORKSPACE:

1. product_recommendations
   - id (UUID)
   - recommendation_number (REC-2025-001)
   - version (01, 02, 03...)
   - enquiry_id (from GHL)
   - client_id
   - company_id
   - created_by_user_id (VA user ID)
   - created_at
   - submitted_date
   - status (Draft, Submitted, Converted to Quote)
   - notes

2. recommendation_sections
   - id (UUID)
   - recommendation_id
   - app_type_id (nullable)
   - custom_section_name (nullable)
   - sort_order

3. recommendation_items
   - id (UUID)
   - recommendation_section_id
   - product_id
   - area_sqm
   - waste_percent (from products table)
   - packs_required (calculated)
   - notes

