5. PREMIER USER WORKFLOW - QUOTE FROM RECOMMENDATION
â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

WHEN: Premier user reviews a submitted Product Recommendation

LOCATION: src/app/quotes/from-recommendation/[id]/page.tsx

PROCESS:
1. Load recommendation data (client, sections, products, areas, packs)
2. Pre-populate Add Quote form with recommendation data
3. Premier adds:
   - Pricing tier (Retail/Trade/VIP/Custom)
   - Labour rate (default $3.00/mÂ²)
   - Custom discounts
   - Quote validity period
4. System automatically:
   - Applies markup to products
   - Generates labour rows (area Ã— $1.50 cost, area Ã— $3.00 sell)
   - Calculates totals with GST 15%
   - Shows margins
5. Premier generates PDF (Template A or B)
6. Premier sends to client
7. Recommendation status â†’ "Converted to Quote"

QUOTE NUMBERING:
- Recommendation: REC-2025-001.01
- Converted Quote: Q-2025-001.01
- Link: quotes.recommendation_id = product_recommendations.id

