- Cancelled: Red

CREATE JOB:
- From accepted quote (button on quote detail page)
- OR manually (src/app/jobs/new/page.tsx)

JOB DETAIL PAGE:
Location: src/app/jobs/[id]/page.tsx
Sections:
- Job info (dates, crew, status)
- Client details
- Quoted items vs actual items used
- Photos (before/after)
- Completion certificate
- Invoice generation

DATABASE:
- jobs table (see schema in document)
- job_line_items (actual materials used)
- job_photos
- completion_certificates

