7. INVOICES PAGE
â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

LOCATION: src/app/invoices/page.tsx

LAYOUT: Same structure as Quotes/Jobs pages

COLUMNS:
- Action (View/Edit/Download PDF)
- Invoice # (sortable, clickable)
- Job # (linked)
- Customer Name
- Company
- Invoice Date
- Due Date
- Amount Ex GST
- GST Amount
- Total Inc GST
- Status (Draft/Sent/Paid/Overdue)
- Payment Method

FEATURES:
- Fuzzy search
- Status filter
- Date range filter
- Overdue highlighting (red)
- Pagination
- Export to Xero/MYOB

ACTION BUTTONS:
[+ New Invoice] [Import] [Export] [Send Reminders]

STATUS BADGES:
- Draft: Gray
- Sent: Blue
- Paid: Green
- Overdue: Red

INVOICE GENERATION:
- Auto-generated from completed job
- Uses actual materials from job_line_items
- Includes labour
- GST 15%
- Payment terms (e.g., 30 days)

INVOICE PDF:
Similar to Quote PDF but includes:
- Invoice # and date
- Due date
- Payment instructions
- Bank account details
- "PAID" stamp if paid

