Each card opens a modal with:

1. USERS & ROLES
   - Add/edit users
   - Assign roles (Admin, Sales Rep, VA, Viewer)
   - Set permissions
   - Password reset

2. APPLICATION TYPES
   - Add/edit application types
   - Set hex color codes
   - Reorder list
   - Activate/deactivate

3. PRICING TIERS
   - Retail markup % (default 60%)
   - Trade markup % (default 40%)
   - VIP markup % (default 25%)
   - Custom tier options

4. QUOTE TEMPLATES
   - Edit PDF header/footer
   - Company logo upload
   - Template A/B preview
   - Email templates

5. SALES REPS
   - Add/edit sales reps
   - Commission rates
   - Contact info
   - Active/inactive status

6. SYSTEM SETTINGS
   - Company details
   - GST rate (15%)
   - Default waste % (10%)
   - Default labour rate ($3.00/mÂ²)
   - Quote validity days (30)
   - Email settings
   - Backup/restore

7. TERMS & CONDITIONS
   - Rich text editor (Quill or TinyMCE)
   - Version control
   - View history
   - Activate/deactivate versions

8. ADVANCED
   - Database backup
   - Import/export data
   - API keys
   - Webhook settings (GHL)
   - Logs viewer

