11. FILE STRUCTURE STANDARDS
â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

CRITICAL RULES:
1. Supabase client: src/lib/supabase.ts (NOT in src/app/lib/)
2. All page imports: import { supabase } from '@/lib/supabase';
3. Page files MUST be named: page.tsx (Next.js requirement)
4. Folder names can be descriptive (e.g., new)

