12. COMMON ISSUES & SOLUTIONS
â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

ISSUE 1: Module not found '@/lib/supabase'
SOLUTION:
1. Verify file exists at: src/lib/supabase.ts
2. Use import: import { supabase } from '@/lib/supabase';
3. Check tsconfig.json has: "baseUrl": ".", "paths": { "@/*": ["./src/*"] }
4. Restart dev server: Ctrl+C, then npm run dev

ISSUE 2: Page not loading (404)
SOLUTION:
1. Verify file is named: page.tsx (not add-quote-page.tsx)
2. Check folder structure matches URL
3. Clear .next cache: rm -rf .next

ISSUE 3: Import path keeps changing
SOLUTION:
Use ABSOLUTE imports everywhere: import { supabase } from '@/lib/supabase';
NEVER use relative paths: ../lib/supabase or ../../lib/supabase

ISSUE 4: TypeScript errors
SOLUTION:
1. Ensure all types are defined at top of file
2. Use proper TypeScript syntax
3. Check for missing return types

