14. CRITICAL REMINDERS
â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

1. VAs create RECOMMENDATIONS, not QUOTES
2. Premier creates QUOTES from RECOMMENDATIONS
3. Always verify file locations BEFORE writing code
4. Use absolute imports: @/lib/supabase
5. Page files MUST be named: page.tsx
6. Master template: Blue headers, fuzzy search, filter buttons (not dropdowns)
7. Labour auto-generated: $1.50 cost, $3.00 sell per mÂ²
8. GST: 15% (New Zealand)
9. Waste %: Default 10% from products table
10. Version control on quotes: Q-001.01, Q-001.02, etc.

